and you damn well know it.

79
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,232
<i>Get outta here!</i>

80
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,510
- Thanks, Charlie.
- That's just crap!

81
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:35,030
