- Bobby, start when you got sick.

89
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:57,318
Nina, it's his story. Let him work it out.

90
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,476
<i>No, no, no. I know what's important here.</i>

91
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,556
Everything starts when he got sick.

92
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,750
