- Nina, please. Don't.

93
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,678
No, I think we should start when
they booed me off the stage.

94
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,757
<i>Nobody's gonna come see
you get booed off the stage.</i>

95
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:12,075
