96
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,714
How do you know
what people will come to see, Boom-Boom?

97
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:18,116
<i>- When did you become the big expert?
- You tell him, Bobby.</i>

98
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:22,153
<i>As long as I've known you,
as far as you're concerned, I am the expert.</i>

99
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,679
<i>BOY: Bullshit!</i>

100
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:33,518
- Who was that?
- That's the kid playing him as a kid.

101
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,915
<i>- Get down from there, kid.
CREW: I'll sort this out.</i>

102
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:38,872
<i>- We're not ready for you yet.
- Take five.</i>

103
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,514
- Wait. I wanna hear what he has to say.
- Jesus Christ!

104
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,356
What did you just say, kid?

105
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,709
I said that's bullshit.

106
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:51,116
- What's bullshit?
- That you know him better than anybody.

107
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:54,470
Great. A miniature version of you,
and he's a method actor.

108
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,112
<i>I need a drink.</i>

109
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,628
- He looks just like him.
- I know, it looks like him.

110
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:03,956
- I'll be back.
DAVID: Here we go again.

111
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:18,350
