112
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:22,837
- I am you.
- You think you got me down?

113
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,075
I know you better than they do.

114
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,554
We could do it 100 times,
it'd never be good enough.

115
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:30,160
It's OK if he yells at me,
but not at the other guys.

116
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,714
They've been working their asses off, man.

117
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:35,115
I've never worked
with such an arrogant asshole.

118
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,157
Listen, you prick.

119
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:42,273
There are four people here who can't be fired.
You're not one of 'em.

120
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:45,392
