127
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,436
<i>on the street where I grew up,</i>

128
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:25,870
<i>with my sister Nina, my brother-in-law Charlie,</i>

129
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:30,152
<i>and, to me, the greatest
